OL,7,FOxford University research has found
OL,8,Fheart scans could help thousands of
OL,9,Fpeople avoid unnecessary invasive
OL,10,Fprocedures.
OL,12,FAccording to a study, an MRI could
OL,13,Fchange how doctors treat at least half
OL,14,Fof patients.
OL,16,FAround 50,000 people are admitted to
OL,17,Fhospital annually with suspected heart
OL,18,Fattacks, those at risk are currently
OL,19,Frecommended to have a coronary
OL,20,Fangiogram.
