OL,7,F"It's vital that we can get everyone
OL,8,Fon a path to receive the tests and
OL,9,Ftreatment they need as quickly as
OL,10,Fpossible to save and improve more
OL,11,Flives.
OL,13,F"Invasive procedures like coronary
OL,14,Fangiograms will continue to have a
OL,15,Fcrucial role in heart care, delivering
OL,16,Fimportant treatments such as stents
OL,17,Fthat can help to save lives and stop
OL,18,Ffuture heart attacks.
